The '''Ulta Center''' was a high-security, luxurious conference center in the city of [[Dal (city)|Dal]] on [[Rondai-2]]. The compound, containing a rooftop landing pad and multiple wings for private gatherings, played host to secret meetings for corporate guests and diplomats.<ref name="Secrets of the Jedi">[[Secrets of the Jedi (novel)|''Secrets of the Jedi'']]</ref>

